A demo of a Single Page Web App with fallback and a jPlayer based player and playlist.

This demo allows uninterrupted playback of audio throughout the site. A static version of the site is available for non-JS enabled agents such as search engines, with minimal code and content repetition.
              
More Info
---------

Blog Post - The Future of Web Apps - Single Page Applications: http://happyworm.com/blog/2010/08/23/the-future-of-web-apps-single-page-applications/

Demo : http://happyworm.com/jPlayerLab/single-page-app/  

Tech : JS, jQuery, jPlayer, HTML, CSS, PHP 